Lionel Messi is the greatest player in the world, perhaps of all time, and after a few minor adjustments Argentina will be on their way to winning the World Cup.

That is how life looks inside the self-deceptive bubble which this Messi band of brothers inhabit.

Alejandro Sabella tells it thus: ‘Whatever Messi does or doesn’t do in this World Cup he is the greatest player in the world and one of the greatest in the history of football.’

