Sabella admitted only: ‘Maybe we made one or two errors and I got one or two things wrong. But we will get better.’

Complacency is contagious in this camp but at least Messi did not appear too gravely affected when he observed: ‘Yes, we do have to improve.’

He can say that again. And he had better keep doing so if the tens of thousands of Argentines – some of whom managed to break into the Maracana without tickets on Sunday – are not to be disappointed.

 

